                    <div>‡§ï‡•Å‡§≤ ‡§ì‡§µ‡§∞: <span id="totalOvers">20</span></div>
                    <div>‡§¨‡•à‡§ü‡§ø‡§Ç‡§ó ‡§∏‡•ç‡§ü‡•ç‡§∞‡§æ‡§á‡§ï: <span id="strike">‡§ü‡•Ä‡§Æ 1</span></div>
                </div>
                <div class="commentary" id="commentary">
                    <div class="commentary-text">‡§ó‡•á‡§Æ ‡§∂‡•Å‡§∞‡•Ç ‡§π‡•Å‡§Ü!</div>
